        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 4 at 1:36AM CDT until June 4 at 2:00AM CDT by NWS Fort Worth TX</headline>
        <description>At 135 AM CDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from Bend to San Saba, moving south at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage to
roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Nix, Bend, Lometa, Us-190 Near The San Saba-
Lampasas County Line, and Colorado Bend State Park.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection stay inside a sturdy structure and keep away from
windows.</instruction>
